Package jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.results

Defines a Java object model for the elements, types, and attributes that compose the OVAL Results.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ClassDirectivesType The ClassDirectives presents a set of flags that describe what information has been included in the results document for a specific OVAL Definition class.
CriteriaResultElement An abstract base class for the criteria-related types.
CriteriaResultLeafElement An abstract base class for the criteria-related leaf types.
CriteriaType The CriteriaResult describes the high level container for all the tests and represents the meat of the definition.
CriterionType The CriterionResult identifies a specific test that is included in the definition's criteria.
DefaultDirectivesType The DefaultDirectives presents the default set of flags that describe what information has been included in the results document.
DefinitionsType The DefinitionsType is a container for one or more Definition instances.
DefinitionType The DefinitionResult holds the result of the evaluation of an OVAL Definition.
DirectivesType The Directives presents a set of flags that describe what information has been included in the results document.
DirectiveType An individual directive element determines whether or not a specific type of result is included in the results document.
ExtendDefinitionType The ExtendDefinitionResult identifies a specific definition that has been extended by the criteria.
OvalResults The OvalResults represents an OVAL Results Document.
ResultsElement An abstract base class for types which represent test results.
ResultsType The SystemResult is a container for one or more SystemResult instances.
SystemType The SystemResult holds the evaluation results of the definitions and tests, as well as a copy of the OVAL System Characteristics used to perform the evaluation.
TestedItemType The TestedItem holds a reference to a system characteristic item that matched the object specified in a test.
TestedVariableType The TestedVariable holds the value to a variable used during the evaluation of a test.
TestsType The TestResults is a container for one or more test instances.
TestType The TestResult provides a reference to every item that matched the object section of the original test as well as providing an overall test result based on those items.
 

Enum Summary
ContentEnumeration The Content enumeration defines the valid values for the directives controlling the amount of expected depth found in the results document.
ResultEnumeration The Result enumeration defines the acceptable result values for the DefinitionResult, CriteriaResult, CriterionResult, ExtendDefinitionResult, TestResult, and TestedItem constructs.
 

Package jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.results Description

Defines a Java object model for the elements, types, and attributes that compose the OVAL Results.
